ly suppress AF order in $S$ = 1/2 or 1\njunctions, as well as in half-filled Hubbard junctions, but reduce rather than\nsuppress AF order in $S$ = 3/2 or 2 junctions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 04:56:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
