nd $\\tau$ to\nestimate whether the ejecta is lanthanide-rich or not.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 07:13:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Nov 2015 21:48:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-23"}
