king a much closer distance for HLX-1 is\nnot a viable solution to this problem, as it introduces other, more serious\ninconsistencies with the observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 09:20:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 05:48:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-23"}
